hotelDescription: Previously the world's tallest hotel (2nd tallest since November 2012), the Rose Rayhaan by Rotana is an iconic building standing 333 meters high on Sheikh Zayed Road. This four star hotel offers convenient accommodation close to the Downtown area, home to the famous Burj Khalifa, Dubai Fountain, and Dubai Mall, one of the world's largest shopping and entertainment destinations. The DIFC Business Centre is also located nearby. The modern rooms and suites provide panoramic city views and amenities such as kitchenette, LCD satellite TV and WiFi connectivity. The hotel's fitness centre includes a large gym, sauna, steam room, jacuzzi, aerobics room and massage services. The outdoor pool on the fourth floor provides views of the Dubai skyline. A variety of international cuisine is available at the hotels main restaurant, whilst snacks and refreshments are offered at the lobby lounge and poolside cafe. Please note the Rose Rayhaan by Rotana is an alcohol-free hotel.

hotelDescription: The Meydan is a five star luxury hotel overlooking the Meydan Racecourse. The 284 rooms and suites are equipped with a working desk, LCD plasma TV with 5.1 surround sound, free WiFi access and complimentary tea and coffee making facilities. Some rooms feature a kitchenette and dining area, and most offer panoramic views of the racetrack. There is a dedicated ladies floor at the hotel with all female staff. The hotel has 7 different food and beverage outlets, including a specialist steakhouse and a poolside bar. Meals can also be served on the outdoor terrace which overlooks the racetrack. The hotel has an extensive spa offering a range of treatments and massage services. Other leisure amenities include a rooftop infinity pool, tennis courts, access to a gold course, a state-of-the-art gymnasium and a variety fitness classes. Guests can also take a guided tour of the stables at Meydan Grandstand. The Meydan hotel is located just a 20 minute drive from the Dubai International Airport.
name: THE MEYDAN HOTEL
